<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<meta content="text/html; charset=utf-8" http-equiv="Content-Type">
	<style>
	     html, body {
	       height: 100%;
	     }

	     html {
	       display: table;
	       margin: auto;
	       font-family: "open sans";
	     }

	     body {
	       display: table-cell;
         -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
	       padding: 0;
	       margin: 0;
         padding-top: 100px;
	       box-sizing: border-box;
	       position: relative;
	       overflow-x: hidden;
         background-color: #362F26;
         background: #362F26;
	     }

	     #banner {
	       max-width: 600px;
         width: 95%
	     }

       #footer {
         width: 20%;
         display:block;
         margin:auto;
         padding: 50px;
       }

	     .notice {
	       max-width: 600px;
         width: 95%;
	       padding: 0 15px;
	       -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
	       color: #FAE2A4;
         opacity: .8;
	     }

	     #hey {
	       color: #D4B166;
	       -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
	       margin-top: 50px;
	       padding: 0 15px;
	     }

	     #image-wrap {
	       max-width: 600px;
         width: 95%;
         margin:0 auto;
	     }

       img {
         padding-left: 15px;
       }

	     #from {
	       color: #D4B166;
	       padding-bottom: 15px;
	       padding-top: 0;
         margin:0;
	     }

       #note {
         color: #D4B166;
         padding-top: 15px;
         padding-bottom: 5px;
         margin: 0;
       }

       h5 {
         margin-left: 25px;
       }

	     .indent {
	       padding-left: 10px;
	     }

	     .general {
         margin-top: 45px;
	       padding: 0 15px;
         color: #D4B166;
	     }

       strong {
         color: #D4B166;
         opacity: 1 !important;
       }

	     li {
	       /*text-indent: -1em;*/
	       /*margin-left: 1em;*/
         color: #FAE2A4;
         opacity: .8;
	       list-style-image: url("https://17.spartahack.com/assets/diamond-w-shadow-4c3fbce6475192408710dec21d88dad2da7004e7a4a9a00e673d608dab81ce07.svg");
	     }

       .a-wrap {
         margin-bottom: 10px;
       }

       a {
         color: #FAE2A4;
         position: relative;
         text-decoration: none;
         padding-bottom: 7px;
         transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
       }

       a:after {
         content: "";
         position: absolute;
         bottom: 2px;
         left: 0;
         height: 1px;
         width: 95%;
         background: #B58A2D,;
         background: linear-gradient(to left, #FAE2A4 0%, #B58A2D 100%);
       }

       a:visited {
         color: #FAE2A4;
       }

       a:hover {
         opacity: 0.7;
       }

	     .main-li {
	       padding-bottom: 5px;
	     }

       #checkin-qr-head {
         color: #FAE2A4;
         text-align: center;
         margin-top: 100px;
         margin-bottom: 25px;
       }

       #qr-wrap {
         margin: 100px auto;
         margin-top: 0px;
         background: white;
         width: 277px;
         padding-top: 10px;
         padding-bottom: 10px;
       }

	     pre {
	         font-family: "Courier 10 Pitch", Courier, monospace;
	         font-size: 100%;
           padding-top: 15px;
           padding-left: 10px;
           background: #696969;
           border: 1px solid #696969;
           border-radius: 5px;
	     }

       #second {
         margin-top: 60px;
       }

	</style>
	<title></title>
</head>
<body>
	<div id="image-wrap" style="max-width: 600px; width: 95%;">
    <%= image_tag attachments['banner.png'].url, :id => 'banner' %>

		<div>
			<h2 id="hey">Hey <%= @name.capitalize %>,</h2>
			<p class="notice" id="first">SpartaHack is almost here! Here are some things you'll need to know:</p>
			<h3 class="general">General Info</h3>
			<ul>
				<li class="main-li">Location: Wells Hall, 619 Red Cedar Road, East Lansing, MI 49924</li>
				<li class="main-li">Parking: Free after 4:00pm in Ramp 5 - but <strong>don't</strong> park on the first floor, and avoid pay-by-plate spaces and 24-hour reserved spots</li>
				<li style="display: inline">
					<pre>WiFi SSID:    SpartaHack
Password:     SpartansWill
      </pre>
				</li>
				<li>Your new favorite site: <a href="https://live.spartahack.com">live.spartahack.com</a>
				</li>
				<li style="display: inline">
					<ul class="indent">
						<li>Detailed schedule</li>
						<li>Parking details</li>
						<li>Venue Map</li>
						<li>Prizes</li>
						<li>Hardware</li>
						<li>Announcements</li>
						<li>FAQ</li>
						<li>Resources</li>
					</ul>
				</li>
			</ul>
			<h3 class="general">Check In</h3>
			<ul>
				<li class="main-li">6:00pm - 8:30pm on Friday, 1/20</li>
				<li class="main-li">If you arrive after that, you can check in at the Help Desk.</li>
				<li class="main-li">You must have a <strong>completed RSVP</strong> to check in.</li>
				<li class="main-li">Hate long lines? Have your QR code loaded on your phone for one-step check-in.</li>
				<li class="main-li">You can also download our iOS, Android, or Windows mobile app to access your QR code and receive push notifications throughout the event.</li>
				<li class="main-li"><strong>Minors: if you are under 18 years of age, we cannot check you in without signed copies of these three documents:</strong></li>
				<li style="list-style: none; display: inline">
					<ul class="indent">
						<li class="a-wrap">
							<a href="https://drive.google.com/open?id=0B57ET4MXSSx3c2pmOW5paWRoUzQ" target="_blank">Medical Release Form</a>
						</li>
						<li class="a-wrap">
							<a href="https://drive.google.com/open?id=0B57ET4MXSSx3cXVWTjVYM2dkNTA" target="_blank">Media Release Form</a>
						</li>
						<li class="a-wrap">
							<a href="https://drive.google.com/open?id=0B57ET4MXSSx3bnYtOWZxZVp3ZVE" target="_blank">Parental Permission Form</a>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</li>
			</ul>

      <p id="checkin-qr-head">Here is your check-in QR code:</p>
      <div id="qr-wrap">
        <%= image_tag attachments['qr.png'].url %>
      </div>

      <h3 class="general">What to bring</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>A valid form of ID (passport if international)</li>
        <li>Laptop and charger</li>
        <li>Toiletries and a change of clothes</li>
        <li>Optional: pillow and blanket</li>
      </ul>

      <h5>
        <strong>
          DON'T BRING: Weapons, alcohol, or other illicit substances.
        </strong>
      </h5>

      <h3 class="general">Travel Reimbursement</h3>
      <li>You are eligible for the amount of travel reimbursement indicated in our travel policy if and only if:</li>
      <ul>
        <li>You and anyone with whom you are carpooling have RSVPed.</li>
        <li>You follow all of the steps in our travel policy.</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="notice" id="second">If you have any questions, please check out the FAQ section of <a href="https://live.spartahack.com">live.spartahack.com</a> or email <a href="mailto:hello@spartahack.com">hello@spartahack.com</a>.</p>
      <p id="note">See you soon! ðŸ˜Š</p>
      <p id="from">- The SpartaHack Team</p>
		</div>
    <%= image_tag attachments['footer.png'].url, :id => 'footer' %>
	</div>
</body>
</html>
